								<path
									d="M7.29412 10.44V2.27333L10.3824 5.77333L10.8235 5.33333L7 1L3.17647 5.33333L3.61765 5.77333L6.70588 2.27333V10.44H7.29412ZM2 11H2.58824V12.3333H11.4118V11H12V13H2V11Z"
